<br>
We tried Terris and got her to about 30% on our first try.  30 minutes later we took our second shot (with a freshly modified battle plan) and we spanked her.<br>
<br>
Of course, the funniest thing I remember was shortly after PoP came out we tried the behemoth encounter with absolutely no idea what to expect.  It was pretty funny seeing an entire 60 person raid force pop in to the guild bind point within like 3 seconds of each other (and within just a few seconds of engaging the boss)  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I think it took us about 10 minutes to stop laughing. <p><table border="0" width="568">
